    public class CollisionHandler

      • beginContact

        public void beginContact(org.jbox2d.dynamics.contacts.Contact contact)
        Defines the way the collision are handled. This specific method is called at the start of a contact : we know at least one of the fixtures involved in the contact is a garbage, as only the garbages moves. So if one of the fixture is a trashcan, the other is a garbage, and it must be destryed. We don't destroy the garbage in this method because it can cause some NullPointerException.
        Specified by:
        beginContact in interface org.jbox2d.callbacks.ContactListener
        Parameters:
        contact - the contact to manage.
